 class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住成班走去大型電器鋪 瘋搶平幾舊既iPhone X<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nsorry iPhone X用家已經玩左1年face ID<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到左今日網上流傳Xs上網/wifi信號差 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲有有部分仲係用LG 垃圾mon 一開盒就綠線 今年又要玩抽獎了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 反而X就無乜問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不嬲iPhone代代都會有唔同既問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無話白唔白老鼠機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n白老鼠機論撚/觀望撚崩潰了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上年個9個無用過face id 都插face id廢 得X用家體驗過出聲 覺得用落體驗好爽 e家face id開始普及 又吹奏返face id<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幾年後個個用face id個陣就會擺X上神台嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成班跟風講褲袋解鎖論<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 笑死"},{"pid":"f484c12270cd0efaa68e1af8785abda061307515","tid":835893,"uid":25612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"910c5282b98ea2b7991a2c11db421289fa8eba06","tid":835893,"uid":109383,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82c6e40315ca1665d536d520b5d353eb66fb8b92","tid":835893,"uid":25612,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9b30308f05740cb6c9da0eaf3359cf144efaa8d4","tid":835893,"uid":609,"like":5,"dislike":37,"score":-32,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T12:39:27.000Z","msg":"8plus 笑而不語<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當初買佢真係好明智 第二日開賣就減三百 六千幾蚊就有<br />\n<br />\n依家仲係又核電又順又唔熱<br />\n<br />\n上埋ios12根本就無敵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n等下一兩代有touch ID under screen先換機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> faceID不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/n